msgid ""
"All beans in the application context are available as predefined variables "
"with their common bean name. This includes standard context beans such as "
"`environment` (of type `org.springframework.core.env.Environment`) as well "
"as `systemProperties` and `systemEnvironment` (of type `Map<String, "
"Object>`) for access to the runtime environment."
msgstr ""

